title: Northwest Trek MIXTAPE
description:
This is a mix tape compiled by some of the best talents and tongues in and around the great Northwest. Download, sit back, and enjoy this ride through the Evergreen state. 

Track 1 - Intro - Thunderchief
Track 2 - Drive In The Rain - Castroni & Greg Double
Track 3 - Hang It Up - Krisis & K Deazy
Track 4 - Dex Dance - 5:ive 3:re
Track 5 - New Life - Thunderchief & Cam The Viking
Track 6 - Idol On Survival - DJ DP
Track 7 - Pray - Enasnimi ft. Shay Dubb
Track 8 - Learn From The Cost - Greg Double, Thunderchief, Mr. Tactical & Skrilla
Track 9 - Lullabies of Love & Lies - Rellic Tha Holy One
Track 10 - Hidden Stash - Deadly Poets
Track 11 - Sinister - Mister Sinister
Track 12 - Say WA - Greg Double, 5:ive 3:re & Awall aka 2piece
Track 13 - Last Laugh (Remixxx) - Enasnimi
Track 14 - It's Whatever - Thunderchief
Track 15 - Menstrual Vodka - Majik Sevenoneoh
Track 16 - Absent - Mr. Tactical, Thunderchief, LST Lost Soul, Convic, Cam The Viking      & Greg Double
BONUS TRACK - Dj Sith The Wicked - Watch Your Back[vs]Black Smoke
